<section class="food-demo" aria-label="食物与静物布置示意图">
  <div class="food-demo__grid">
    <div class="food-demo__card">
      <div class="food-demo__badge">先清桌面</div>
      <div class="food-demo__scene food-demo__scene--table">
        <div class="food-demo__plate">主体</div>
        <div class="food-demo__noise food-demo__noise--cup">杂物</div>
        <div class="food-demo__noise food-demo__noise--box">包装</div>
      </div>
      <p>静物和食物的第一步常常不是调色，而是把无关物件移开，让主体先变干净、明确。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="food-demo__card">
      <div class="food-demo__badge">窗边光 + 配色统一</div>
      <div class="food-demo__scene food-demo__scene--light">
        <div class="food-demo__window"></div>
        <div class="food-demo__plate food-demo__plate--light">主体</div>
        <div class="food-demo__accent">配件</div>
      </div>
      <p>食物和静物最容易出质感的组合，通常是简单背景、柔和侧光和不乱的色彩关系。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

